snippet.title: No Creeps Were Harmed TD - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's your look at the announcement trailer for No Creeps Were Harmed TD, an upcoming tower defense game coming to Steam.

In No Creeps Were Harmed TD, employ lethal turrets, traps, and gadgets to defend against an onslaught of evolving creeps! Step into a twisted, hyper 3D, mind-bending realm. Upgrade and adapt your defenses. Become a master maze crafter. Collect bizarre artifacts. Rush creeps for lucrative rewards, and succumb to greed.
